A '''oath rigora''' was a type of [[rigora]]. An oath rigora could only end in [[Death/Legends|death]] and was declared by swearing an oath. Oath rigoras were often longstanding, and many senior [[Phosphura Belt Pirates|Belt Pirates]] had unfinished oath rigoras with hostile fellow [[Pirate/Legends|pirates]].<ref name="Zirtran's Anchor (article)">{{JournalCite|5|Zirtran's Anchor (article)}}</ref>

